Name: Access Team Project Settings and Refresh Script Repository
Description: Navigate to the team project settings, access script repositories, refresh the script repository, and verify the home page.
Test Steps:
Step 1: Navigate to team/*/project/*
Step 2: Click on link teamProjectSettings -> Navigate to page 'team/*/project/*/settings'
Step 3: Click on link teamProjectScriptRepositories -> Navigate to page 'team/*/project/*/test-project'
Step 4: Click on link teamProjectTestProject -> Navigate to page 'team/*/project/*/test-project/*'
Step 5: Click on button refreshScriptRepository -> Navigate to page ''
Step 6: Take full page screenshot as checkpoint

Name: Access User Settings and Katalon API Key
Description: Navigate to the organization home, access user settings, and retrieve the Katalon API key, then verify the home page.
Test Steps:
Step 1: Navigate to organization/*/home
Step 2: Click on button qa
Step 3: Click on link userSettings -> Navigate to page 'user/*'
Step 4: Click on link katalonApiKey -> Navigate to page ''
Step 5: Take full page screenshot as checkpoint

Name: Manage Script Repository and Schedule Test Run in Team Project
Description: Access team project settings, manage script repositories, schedule a test run, and verify the home page after actions.
Test Steps:
Step 1: Navigate to team/*/project/*
Step 2: Click on link teamProjectSettings -> Navigate to page 'team/*/project/*/settings'
Step 3: Click on link teamProjectScriptRepositories -> Navigate to page 'team/*/project/*/test-project'
Step 4: Click on button typeAll
Step 5: Click on link teamProjectCreate
Step 6: Click on link teamProjectZipRepo -> Navigate to page 'team/*/project/*/test-project/*'
Step 7: Click on button edit
Step 8: Click on button refreshScriptRepository
Step 9: Click on button cancel
Step 10: Click on button scheduleTestRun -> Navigate to page 'team/*/project/*/test-planning'
Step 11: Click on button closeDialog
Step 12: Click on link teamProjectSchedules -> Navigate to page 'team/*/project/*/grid'
Step 13: Click on button scriptRepositoryAll -> Navigate to page ''
Step 14: Take full page screenshot as checkpoint
